                <h1>How to Easily Close Apps on iPhone 13</h1>
                <p>To close apps on your iPhone 13, swipe up from the bottom of the screen and pause in the middle. This opens the App Switcher, showcasing all your open apps. Swipe left or right to find the app you want to close, then swipe it up and off the screen. This helps enhance your device's performance and battery life.</p>
